Hate on Elon Musk as a person as much as you want. He deserves it. Don’t want him to be rich? Too fucking bad. He did what we want. He made EVs and green energy viable. Nobody else did. You can’t incentivize something crazy hard then complain when someone actually does it.

A real “Green New Deal” isn’t anti-capitalist. It’s about directing the tool that is capitalism at the problem. The result? It’s Tesla. It’s jobs making EVs, it’s batteries, and it’s mining + refining materials for green energy. Ideally it’s nuclear, too.
